asyncDefine("ch04-technical-03-exercises-03-highlighters",function(){return function(){return'<article><section><h2 id="select-to-highlight">Select to Highlight</h2>\n<h3 id="description">Description</h3>\n<p><strong>Select-to-Highlight</strong> (<code>+select-to-highlight</code>) is a type of exercise where the user\ncan select and deselect elements. Selected elements recieve a class (see <code>selectedClass</code> below).\nYou can have any kind of content, as long as the <code>good</code> and <code>bad</code> CSS classes are used.</p>\n<h3 id="parameters">Parameters</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>scoreN</code>: N from the scoring section below. defaults to the number of <em>good</em> elements</li>\n<li><code>startingScore</code>: the score before clicking on anything. defaults to <code>0</code></li>\n<li><code>selectedClass</code>: the class to add to selected elements. defaults to <code>selected</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id="scoring">Scoring</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Score starts at <code>startingScore</code></li>\n<li>Each selected <em>good</em> element adds 100/N to the score</li>\n<li>Each selected <em>bad</em> element substracts 100/N from the score</li>\n<li>Score cannot be lower than 0</li>\n<li>Score cannot be higher than 100</li>\n<li>If <code>scoreN</code> and <code>startingScore</code> are left to their defaults, the score is 100 when all <em>good</em> elements are selected and no <em>bad</em> element is selected</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id="example-source-">Example (source)</h3>\n<pre><code class="lang-jade">+exercise({name:&#39;ch03-highlighters-e1&#39;)\n  +statement\n    h4 Exercise: Final &#39;a&#39;\n    .progress-box\n    | Click or tap  letter &lt;strong&gt;a&lt;/strong&gt; at the end of the words below.\n  +select-to-highlight\n      div\n        span.bad mamm\n        span.good a\n      div\n        span.bad Ann\n        span.good a\n      div\n        span.bad pupil\n      div\n        span.bad parent\n      div\n        span.bad principal</code></pre>\n<p>Rendered sample:</p><script>var ex_859497814 = Exercises.push(new Exercises.Exercise(859497814, \'{"name":"ch03-highlighters-e1"}\'));\n</script><div id="ex_859497814" class="exercise"><div class="statement"><h4>Exercise: Final \'a\'</h4><div class="progress-box"></div>Click or tap  letter <strong>a</strong> at the end of the words below.</div><script>var ex_336867611 = Exercises.push(new Exercises.SelectToHighlight(336867611, \'\'));\n</script><div id="ex_336867611" class="select-to-highlight"><div><span class="bad">mamm</span><span class="good">a</span></div><div><span class="bad">Ann</span><span class="good">a</span></div><div><span class="bad">pupil</span></div><div><span class="bad">parent</span></div><div><span class="bad">principal</span></div></div><script>Exercises.pop();</script></div><script>Exercises.pop();</script><p>As long as there are &#39;bad&#39; and &#39;good&#39; divs, anything can go inside, including divs and images</p>\n<pre>+exercise({name:\'ch03-highlighters-e2\'})        \n  .progress-box\n  +statement\n    h4 Exercise:  Planets and satellites\n    | Select which one of the following are a satellites in the Solar System\n  +select-to-highlight\n    .row.container\n      .item.bad.col-md-3 Mercury\n        +img(\'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/88/Reprocessed_Mariner_10_image_of_Mercury.jpg\')\n      .item.good.col-md-3 Io\n        +img(\'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7b/Io_highest_resolution_true_color.jpg\')\n      .item.bad.col-md-3 Mars\n        +img(\'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/82/Mars_and_Syrtis_Major_-_GPN-2000-000923.jpg\')\n      .item.good.col-md-3 Phobos\n        +img(\'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5c/Phobos_colour_2008.jpg\')</pre><p>CSS:</p><pre>.ch03-highlighters-e2 .row\n  background-color: #000\n  \n.ch03-highlighters-e2 .item\n  color: #fff\n  margin: 0\n  padding: 5px 10px\n  text-align: center\n  \n.ch03-highlighters-e2 img\n  opacity: .5\n  \n.ch03-highlighters-e2 .item.good.selected img\n  opacity: 1\n  \n.ch03-highlighters-e2 .item.bad.selected img\n  opacity: 0.3\n  </pre><p>Rendered sample:</p><script>var ex_41963555 = Exercises.push(new Exercises.Exercise(41963555, \'{"name":"ch03-highlighters-e2"}\'));\n</script><div id="ex_41963555" class="exercise"><div class="statement"><h4>Exercise:  Planets and satellites</h4><div class="progress-box"></div>Select which one of the following are a satellites in the Solar System\nCurrent score: &nbsp<span class="score-box"></span></div><script>var ex_1984600884 = Exercises.push(new Exercises.SelectToHighlight(1984600884, \'\'));\n</script><div id="ex_1984600884" class="select-to-highlight"><div class="row"><div class="item bad col-md-3">Mercury<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/88/Reprocessed_Mariner_10_image_of_Mercury.jpg"/></div><div class="item good col-md-3">Io<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7b/Io_highest_resolution_true_color.jpg"/></div><div class="item bad col-md-3">Mars<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/82/Mars_and_Syrtis_Major_-_GPN-2000-000923.jpg"/></div><div class="item good col-md-3">Phobos<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5c/Phobos_colour_2008.jpg"/></div></div></div><script>Exercises.pop();</script></div><script>Exercises.pop();</script></section></article>'}});